check_route=$USER1$/check_route -H $HOSTADDRESS$ -P $ARG1$ -S $ARG2$ -C

[name]
check_route

[info]
This plugin checks what route the IP traffic takes.

[why]
To help you keep track of what route is used for certain traffic. You may use the plugin to see what Internet connection your traffic is using at the moment.

[how]
By analyzing the result from a trace made with the command traceroute.

